This project includes and/or builds on work from several other projects:

- The original SquadMaps website by Pablo Ferrer (Napster653) and maintained
  by Matthew Moss (mahtoid). https://github.com/mahtoid/SquadMaps
  Map textures, tile assets, faction flags, and unit icons are derived from
  this upstream and from Squad's game data (© Offworld Industries Ltd.).
  This fork is a community rewrite and not affiliated with squadmaps.com.

- CUE4Parse by FabianFG and contributors, MIT licensed.
  https://github.com/FabianFG/CUE4Parse
  Used as a git submodule by the spatial extractor.

- The progressive RAAS UX design pattern was inspired by squadlanes.com,
  a separate community tool. No code from squadlanes was copied — only the
  user-facing interaction model.

- Squad and all related game assets are © Offworld Industries Ltd. This is
  a fan project; no affiliation with or endorsement by Offworld Industries.
